{"tid":180875,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"ViuTV英文台開播 主力HBO劇有無睇頭？","createTime":"2017-03-31T08:17:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T14:42:24.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1066701b69ab146f43700cd0bc5478cc00691088","tid":180875,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T08:17:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1745000/1748180/0331EC01_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1745000%2F1748180%2F0331EC01_1024.jpg&h=27e699e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nViuTV旗下全新免費英文頻度ViuTVsix96台今天(3月31日）正式啟播，究竟提供甚麼類型節目？<br />\n<br />\n根據其節目表，早上ViuTVsix主要播外購的外國音樂節目、資訊節目及新聞節目。新聞節目方面，有來自CNN、DW News、Aljazeera半島電視台及NHK World等節目，以及ABC長青新聞節目《20/20》。<br />\n<br />\n主打HBO原創劇<br />\n<br />\n晚間節目，主打外購劇集。而據目前資料所見，重頭戲是ViuTVsix和Now TV及HBO聯手合作《NowTV Presents： HBO Originals》。這是HBO歷來首次於亞洲免費頻度推出的品牌時段，逢星期二、三、四、五及日，晚上10時半至11時半，將會播出一系列從未在香港免費電視播出的作品。<br />\n<img src=\"http://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1745000/1748180/viu_Tv_2017_3_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1745000%2F1748180%2Fviu_Tv_2017_3_1024.jpg&h=3fbf096d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">《酒私風雲》是共有56集的史詩式犯罪劇，製作一絲不苟，歷年來共拿下20項艾美獎。(ViuTV6提供)</span><br />\n<br />\n星期日晚開始，率先登場的是連播兩集諷嘲荷里活生態群星客串的喜劇《色慾荷里活》（Entourage）。星期二及三該時段則會播馬田史高西斯(Martin Scorsese)監製的史詩式犯罪劇《酒私風雲》（Boardwalk Empire）。<br />\n<br />\n暫時最吸引的劇集，是星期四出場的《刑警雙雄》(True Detective)。這部由影帝馬修麥康納希(Matthew McConaughey)和活地夏里遜（Woody Harrelson）主演的偵探懸疑劇，曾奪得艾美獎最佳導演獎，是近年HBO最廣受好評之作。以上劇集，ViuTV回覆，暫時只會提供中文字幕，沒有雙語配音。<br />\n<img src=\"http://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1745000/1748180/TrueDetective20170331_01_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1745000%2F1748180%2FTrueDetective20170331_01_1024.jpg&h=54df1197&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">偵探懸疑劇《刑警雙雄》是近年HBO最廣受好評的劇集，將逢星期四晚在VIuTV6播映。（VIuTV6提供）</span><br />\n<br />\n事實上，明珠台播映外購劇集的時段，也就是晚上10時40分至11時35分，而且周一至周五每日各有不同主打。當中包括《魔鬼神探》(Lucifer)、《閃電俠》(The Flash)及《女超人》(Supergirl)及《欲骨查》(Bones)。最可觀的是周四晚現時熱播的《夜班經理》（The Night Manager)。這部由湯希丹斯頓（Tom Hiddleston）和曉治羅利（Hugh Laurie）主演英國間諜短篇劇，已獲2項艾美獎及3項金球獎。<br />\n<br />\n同時段，在Viu TV6則是大受好評的《刑警雙雄》。以上兩部英美劇均是雙雄格局，劇情引人入勝，而且也是首度在免費頻度播出，也是兩台一星期中最有睇頭的劇集。"},{"pid":"5d1c7758442d2096385fded54d9581caaf460b99","tid":180875,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T08:19:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1745000/1748180/nightmanager201703_0003_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1745000%2F1748180%2Fnightmanager201703_0003_1024.jpg&h=d6421376&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">明珠台逢周四晚10時40分播出英國得獎間諜短篇劇《夜班經理》，湯希丹斯頓演技及美男本色大發放。（劇照）</span><br />\n<br />\nViuTV也提及將會播出HBO的反恐動作劇《絕地反擊》(Strike Back)。雖然已公佈的劇集名單, 全部都在HBO播完的舊劇，但喜訊是，以往錯過了這些大有來頭劇集的觀眾，現在正好可以在免費頻道收看。<br />\n<br />\n然而, HBO是收費頻度，以往不少著名出品均有大量裸露及暴力成份，如《真愛如血》（True Blood）及現正熱播的《權力遊戲》(Game of Thrones)，會否也一拼在免費頻度推出，仍是未知之數。希望金句多多的神劇《Newsroom》有機會在ViuTV6播出吧！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1745000/1748180/dogtv20170331_001_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1745000%2F1748180%2Fdogtv20170331_001_1024.jpg&h=360efe40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近年時興寵物及獸醫節目，ViuTV6周六及日也會主打這類節目。(ViuTV6提供)<br />\n<br />\n這全新免費英文頻道也會主打外購的寵物節目，如《Dog TV》及獸醫節目等，主要集中在周六及周日播出。目前ViuTV 6的節目編排陣勢，晚上8時半至9時半主打生活潮流和娛樂資訊節目，跟明珠台的編排近似，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但暫時看來，節目類型就不及明珠台的多元化。會否提供到更多真正選擇給觀眾？仍要拭目以待。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://topick.hket.com/article/1748180/ViuTV%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E5%8F%B0%E9%96%8B%E6%92%AD%20%20%E4%B8%BB%E5%8A%9BHBO%E5%8A%87%E6%9C%89%E7%84%A1%E7%9D%87%E9%A0%AD%EF%BC%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1748180%2FViuTV%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%258F%25B0%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2592%25AD%2520%2520%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%258A%259BHBO%25E5%258A%2587%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%259D%2587%25E9%25A0%25AD%25EF%25BC%259F&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPpUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=96b789cb\" target=\"_blank\">http://topick.hket.com/article/1748180/ViuTV%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E5%8F%B0%E9%96%8B%E6%92%AD%20%20%E4%B8%BB%E5%8A%9BHBO%E5%8A%87%E6%9C%89%E7%84%A1%E7%9D%87%E9%A0%AD%EF%BC%9F</a>"},{"pid":"0b4af3d839615690e0c03b78c5675f24fdba5687","tid":180875,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T08:25:33.000Z","msg":"True Detective去睇番無Cut版好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b8c98cbc40d89c6468c3b53ca6f775770c5093","tid":180875,"uid":43215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T08:36:11.000Z","msg":"希望會播silicon valley"},{"pid":"bf24d727e61f21eb8e43082375af141d592e2686","tid":180875,"uid":44663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T08:36:50.000Z","msg":"Ballers 一刀不剪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7f11db15e5ebdf4349631fc9ab501c87c75ed99","tid":180875,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T08:39:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>希望會播silicon valley</blockquote><br />\n呢套超高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"956730ad77fbc49f81828222bc7115b4a04dbb11","tid":180875,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T08:49:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"032729e6c731e8d3164ea5c1d553887ce8f970ad","tid":180875,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T08:54:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" cla